  "source_text": {
    "text_id": "text_013",
    "title": "《地书》白话版 13点-24点-次日3点",
    "source": "教师提供",
    "raw_text": "13点：我走在斑马线上，心里盘算着给她准备一份生日礼物——她马上就要30岁了。我又想到，要是送她一份求婚礼物，我们就能结婚了，可送什么好呢？她喜欢香奈儿，可我没钱，买不起。走着走着，我看到一家书店，想到书也是个不错的礼物。我走进书店，翻了翻书，突然想到可以在书里夹一朵玫瑰，可玫瑰很快就枯萎了，我的心也跟着碎了。我又想到书里藏着坏人，用枪指着我，有点害怕。坏人开枪打我，我躲开了，有点生气。我看着机票，想去旅行，忍不住笑了。我想到我们结婚后去度蜜月，笑了。我拿起手机给她发消息。我问她：“结婚后想去哪度蜜月？”她回：“想去自由女神像，还有埃菲尔铁塔……”电话响了，我看着机票，想去悉尼歌剧院、富士山、泰姬陵、加拿大、金字塔……最后选了美国。美国的景点有白宫、迪士尼、梦露、体育馆、自由女神像、世贸中心。我想到世贸中心被炸了，有点惊讶。我查了去美国的航班、机场、酒店和攻略。各种酒店都列了出来，五星的、三星的、经济型的，还有博物馆、剧院，各种奢侈品品牌。我点了赞，笑着继续翻书，走着走着到了门口，红灯亮了，停了下来。我想到她，转身往回走，又查了巴黎的景点，巴黎圣母院、蒙娜丽莎、埃菲尔铁塔……到了门口。我刷卡结账，想着买两本书当礼物。付了钱，拿到了礼物，想到她会很开心。我看着礼物，纠结要不要送她。走出书店，想到她的生日，又回头看了看。我想着相机太贵，不买；平板太贵，不买；滑板太贵，不买；游戏不贵，买了，忍不住笑了。我想到她和游戏，还是去结账吧。结完账，走出书店，看了看时间，回公司。刷了工牌，走进电梯，看到快递的牌子，有点惊讶。按了电梯，电梯到了1、2……89楼，红灯停了，开门，出去。左转，直行，转弯，直行，再转弯，直行，打卡，刷手机，开门。走到工位，坐下。24点：午夜十二点，我没有开车，而是选择步行回家。我看着地图，沿着脚下的脚印，一步步向前走。路上很安静，只有我一个人的脚步声。我经过了一个门口，又经过了一个警察局门口。走着走着，我看到一个女人，抬头看了看天空，然后继续往前走。沿着长长的脚印，我终于走到了家。次日3点：凌晨三点，我被蚊子的嗡嗡声吵醒了。我听到外面有人在吵架，感到非常烦躁。我开始用手拍蚊子，并用杀虫剂喷它们，但蚊子总是飞来飞去，很难打到。我关掉电视和灯，准备睡觉，但蚊子还是不停地骚扰我。我打开台灯，继续用杀虫剂和苍蝇拍消灭蚊子。我追着蚊子跑，上下挥舞着杀虫剂，累得满头大汗。最后，我终于打死了一只蚊子，手上沾满了血。我关掉台灯，终于可以安心睡觉了。",
    "notes": "《地书》白话版13点、24点、次日3点文本，用于语境实际含义标注"
  },
  "units": [
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_001",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "13点：我走在斑马线上，心里盘算着给她准备一份生日礼物——她马上就要30岁了。",
      "sentence_index": 1,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 44,
      "children": ["word_001", "word_002", "word_003", "word_004", "word_005"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_002",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我又想到，要是送她一份求婚礼物，我们就能结婚了，可送什么好呢？",
      "sentence_index": 2,
      "char_start": 44,
      "char_end": 80,
      "children": ["word_006", "word_007", "word_008", "word_009"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_003",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "她喜欢香奈儿，可我没钱，买不起。",
      "sentence_index": 3,
      "char_start": 80,
      "char_end": 100,
      "children": ["word_010", "word_011", "word_012"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_004",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走着走着，我看到一家书店，想到书也是个不错的礼物。",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "char_start": 100,
      "char_end": 132,
      "children": ["word_013", "word_014", "word_015", "word_016"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_005",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我走进书店，翻了翻书，突然想到可以在书里夹一朵玫瑰，可玫瑰很快就枯萎了，我的心也跟着碎了。",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "char_start": 132,
      "char_end": 200,
      "children": ["word_017", "word_018", "word_019", "word_020", "word_021"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_006",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我又想到书里藏着坏人，用枪指着我，有点害怕。",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "char_start": 200,
      "char_end": 230,
      "children": ["word_022", "word_023", "word_024"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_007",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "坏人开枪打我，我躲开了，有点生气。",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "char_start": 230,
      "char_end": 255,
      "children": ["word_025", "word_026", "word_027"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_008",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着机票，想去旅行，忍不住笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "char_start": 255,
      "char_end": 280,
      "children": ["word_028", "word_029", "word_030"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_009",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到我们结婚后去度蜜月，笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "char_start": 280,
      "char_end": 305,
      "children": ["word_031", "word_032"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_010",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我拿起手机给她发消息。",
      "sentence_index": 10,
      "char_start": 305,
      "char_end": 322,
      "children": ["word_033", "word_034"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_011",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我问她：“结婚后想去哪度蜜月？”",
      "sentence_index": 11,
      "char_start": 322,
      "char_end": 348,
      "children": ["word_035", "word_036"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_012",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "她回：“想去自由女神像，还有埃菲尔铁塔……”",
      "sentence_index": 12,
      "char_start": 348,
      "char_end": 380,
      "children": ["word_037", "word_038"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_013",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "电话响了，我看着机票，想去悉尼歌剧院、富士山、泰姬陵、加拿大、金字塔……最后选了美国。",
      "sentence_index": 13,
      "char_start": 380,
      "char_end": 445,
      "children": ["word_039", "word_040", "word_041"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_014",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "美国的景点有白宫、迪士尼、梦露、体育馆、自由女神像、世贸中心。",
      "sentence_index": 14,
      "char_start": 445,
      "char_end": 490,
      "children": ["word_042", "word_043"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_015",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到世贸中心被炸了，有点惊讶。",
      "sentence_index": 15,
      "char_start": 490,
      "char_end": 515,
      "children": ["word_044", "word_045"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_016",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我查了去美国的航班、机场、酒店和攻略。",
      "sentence_index": 16,
      "char_start": 515,
      "char_end": 545,
      "children": ["word_046", "word_047"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_017",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "各种酒店都列了出来，五星的、三星的、经济型的，还有博物馆、剧院，各种奢侈品品牌。",
      "sentence_index": 17,
      "char_start": 545,
      "char_end": 605,
      "children": ["word_048", "word_049", "word_050"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_018",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我点了赞，笑着继续翻书，走着走着到了门口，红灯亮了，停了下来。",
      "sentence_index": 18,
      "char_start": 605,
      "char_end": 655,
      "children": ["word_051", "word_052", "word_053"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_019",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到她，转身往回走，又查了巴黎的景点，巴黎圣母院、蒙娜丽莎、埃菲尔铁塔……到了门口。",
      "sentence_index": 19,
      "char_start": 655,
      "char_end": 720,
      "children": ["word_054", "word_055", "word_056"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_020",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我刷卡结账，想着买两本书当礼物。",
      "sentence_index": 20,
      "char_start": 720,
      "char_end": 745,
      "children": ["word_057", "word_058"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_021",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "付了钱，拿到了礼物，想到她会很开心。",
      "sentence_index": 21,
      "char_start": 745,
      "char_end": 775,
      "children": ["word_059", "word_060"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_022",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着礼物，纠结要不要送她。",
      "sentence_index": 22,
      "char_start": 775,
      "char_end": 798,
      "children": ["word_061", "word_062"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_023",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走出书店，想到她的生日，又回头看了看。",
      "sentence_index": 23,
      "char_start": 798,
      "char_end": 830,
      "children": ["word_063", "word_064"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_024",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想着相机太贵，不买；平板太贵，不买；滑板太贵，不买；游戏不贵，买了，忍不住笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 24,
      "char_start": 830,
      "char_end": 890,
      "children": ["word_065", "word_066", "word_067", "word_068"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_025",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我想到她和游戏，还是去结账吧。",
      "sentence_index": 25,
      "char_start": 890,
      "char_end": 915,
      "children": ["word_069", "word_070"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_026",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "结完账，走出书店，看了看时间，回公司。",
      "sentence_index": 26,
      "char_start": 915,
      "char_end": 945,
      "children": ["word_071", "word_072", "word_073"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_027",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "刷了工牌，走进电梯，看到快递的牌子，有点惊讶。",
      "sentence_index": 27,
      "char_start": 945,
      "char_end": 980,
      "children": ["word_074", "word_075", "word_076"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_028",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "按了电梯，电梯到了1、2……89楼，红灯停了，开门，出去。",
      "sentence_index": 28,
      "char_start": 980,
      "char_end": 1025,
      "children": ["word_077", "word_078", "word_079"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_029",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "左转，直行，转弯，直行，再转弯，直行，打卡，刷手机，开门。",
      "sentence_index": 29,
      "char_start": 1025,
      "char_end": 1070,
      "children": ["word_080", "word_081", "word_082"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_030",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走到工位，坐下。",
      "sentence_index": 30,
      "char_start": 1070,
      "char_end": 1085,
      "children": ["word_083", "word_084"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_031",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "24点：午夜十二点，我没有开车，而是选择步行回家。",
      "sentence_index": 31,
      "char_start": 1085,
      "char_end": 1120,
      "children": ["word_085", "word_086", "word_087"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_032",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着地图，沿着脚下的脚印，一步步向前走。",
      "sentence_index": 32,
      "char_start": 1120,
      "char_end": 1155,
      "children": ["word_088", "word_089", "word_090"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_033",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "路上很安静，只有我一个人的脚步声。",
      "sentence_index": 33,
      "char_start": 1155,
      "char_end": 1180,
      "children": ["word_091", "word_092"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_034",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我经过了一个门口，又经过了一个警察局门口。",
      "sentence_index": 34,
      "char_start": 1180,
      "char_end": 1215,
      "children": ["word_093", "word_094"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_035",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走着走着，我看到一个女人，抬头看了看天空，然后继续往前走。",
      "sentence_index": 35,
      "char_start": 1215,
      "char_end": 1260,
      "children": ["word_095", "word_096", "word_097"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_036",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "沿着长长的脚印，我终于走到了家。",
      "sentence_index": 36,
      "char_start": 1260,
      "char_end": 1285,
      "children": ["word_098", "word_099"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_037",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "次日3点：凌晨三点，我被蚊子的嗡嗡声吵醒了。",
      "sentence_index": 37,
      "char_start": 1285,
      "char_end": 1320,
      "children": ["word_100", "word_101"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_038",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我听到外面有人在吵架，感到非常烦躁。",
      "sentence_index": 38,
      "char_start": 1320,
      "char_end": 1345,
      "children": ["word_102", "word_103"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_039",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我开始用手拍蚊子，并用杀虫剂喷它们，但蚊子总是飞来飞去，很难打到。",
      "sentence_index": 39,
      "char_start": 1345,
      "char_end": 1400,
      "children": ["word_104", "word_105", "word_106"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_040",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我关掉电视和灯，准备睡觉，但蚊子还是不停地骚扰我。",
      "sentence_index": 40,
      "char_start": 1400,
      "char_end": 1440,
      "children": ["word_107", "word_108"]
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_001",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "斑马线上",
      "sentence_id": "sent_001",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 1,
      "char_start": 10,
      "char_end": 15
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_002",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "盘算",
      "sentence_id": "sent_001",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 2,
      "char_start": 18,
      "char_end": 21
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_003",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "生日礼物",
      "sentence_id": "sent_001",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 3,
      "char_start": 25,
      "char_end": 30
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_004",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "30岁",
      "sentence_id": "sent_001",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 4,
      "char_start": 38,
      "char_end": 42
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_005",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "她",
      "sentence_id": "sent_001",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 5,
      "char_start": 31,
      "char_end": 32
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_006",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "求婚礼物",
      "sentence_id": "sent_002",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 1,
      "char_start": 55,
      "char_end": 61
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_007",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "结婚",
      "sentence_id": "sent_002",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 2,
      "char_start": 66,
      "char_end": 68
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_008",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "没钱",
      "sentence_id": "sent_003",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 1,
      "char_start": 88,
      "char_end": 90
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_009",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "买不起",
      "sentence_id": "sent_003",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 2,
      "char_start": 91,
      "char_end": 94
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_010",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "香奈儿",
      "sentence_id": "sent_003",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 3,
      "char_start": 83,
      "char_end": 87
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_011",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "书店",
      "sentence_id": "sent_004",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 1,
      "char_start": 118,
      "char_end": 121
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_012",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "书",
      "sentence_id": "sent_004",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 2,
      "char_start": 125,
      "char_end": 126
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_013",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "玫瑰",
      "sentence_id": "sent_005",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 1,
      "char_start": 168,
      "char_end": 171
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_014",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "枯萎",
      "sentence_id": "sent_005",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 2,
      "char_start": 178,
      "char_end": 181
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "word_015",
      "unit_type": "word",
      "text": "坏人",
      "sentence_id": "sent_006",
      "word_index_in_sentence": 1,
      "char_start": 212,
      "char_end": 215
    },
    {
